[COMPONENT BEHAVIOR]

Modal:
- Always trap focus inside modal when open
- Close on backdrop click and on Escape key
- Animate with transition opacity and scale, duration 150ms
- Never stack more than one modal at a time

Form:
- Disable submit button while request is pending
- Show inline error per field, not a global alert
- Reset form after successful submit
- Never clear form on failed submit, preserve user input

Table:
- Always show column headers even when data is empty
- Highlight row on hover with bg-gray-50
- Truncate long text with truncate class, show full text on hover via title attribute
- Amount column always right aligned

Dropdown and Select:
- Always show a placeholder option as the first item, value empty string
- Placeholder text: "Select..." or contextually named
- Never auto-select the first option

Toast / Notification:
- Success: bottom-right, bg-gray-900 text-white, auto dismiss after 3 seconds
- Error: bottom-right, bg-rose-600 text-white, does not auto dismiss, user must close
- Never show more than 2 toasts at once

Navigation:
- Always highlight the active route in sidebar
- Do not use full page reload for navigation, use Next.js Link component
- Sidebar stays visible on all dashboard pages, collapses to icon only on mobile

