[ACCESSIBILITY]

- All images must have an alt attribute. Decorative images use alt=""
- All form inputs must have an associated label using htmlFor and id
- All icon-only buttons must have aria-label
- All modal dialogs must have role="dialog" and aria-modal="true"
- Color alone must never be the only indicator of meaning. Always pair color with text or icon
- Focus ring must be visible on all interactive elements. Never use outline-none without a replacement
- Income and expense amounts must not rely only on color. Use + and - prefix as well

